headline: AlertD Launches Multi-Purpose AI Agentic SRE and DevOps Platform to Transform Cloud Operations
summary: AlertD today launched out of stealth, unveiling its agentic AI SRE (Site Reliability Engineering) and DevOps platform designed to tackle the mounting operational complexity of cloud operations. AlertD empowers teams to quickly get contextualized visibility across their AWS environments through an easy to use user interface that delivers verifiable data and allows for powerful collaboration.

headline: Buy Nvidia stock into this week’s earnings report: Evercore ISI
summary: Investing.com -- Evercore ISI analysts told investors in a note Monday that they are buyers of Nvidia shares ahead of this week’s earnings report, arguing that demand momentum, improving supply and attractive valuation leave the market underestimating the chipmaker’s growth outlook.
